            "name": "Ink and Wash",
            "desc": "<size=40><color=Title>Phantasmic Imprint<\/color><\/size>nZhezhi may summon <color=Highlight>Phantasmic Imprints<\/color> at the cost of Afflatus when casting Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Manifestation<\/color> or Heavy Attack <color=Highlight>Conjuration<\/color>.nUp to 1 of each of <color=Highlight>Phantasmic Imprint - Left<\/color>, <color=Highlight>Phantasmic Imprint - Middle<\/color>, and <color=Highlight>Phantasmic Imprint - Right<\/color> can exist at the same time, each lasting for 15s.n<size=10><\/size>n<size=40><color=Title>Heavy Attack - Conjuration<\/color><\/size>nThe 5 moves below consume STA to perform <color=Highlight>Conjuration<\/color> to attack the target, dealing <color=Ice>Glacio DMG<\/color>.n-Hold the <color=Highlight>Normal Attack button<\/color> shortly after <color=Highlight>Basic Attack Stage 3<\/color>.n-Press the <color=Highlight>Normal Attack button<\/color> shortly after casting Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Manifestation<\/color>.n-Hold the <color=Highlight>Normal Attack button<\/color> shortly after casting Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Stroke of Genius<\/color> or Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Creation's Zenith<\/color>.n-Hold the <color=Highlight>Normal Attack button<\/color> while in mid-air.n-Hold the <color=Highlight>Normal Attack button<\/color> after a successful <color=Highlight>Dodge<\/color>.nIf Zhezhi has at least 30 Afflatus when performing any of these, consume 30 Afflatus to summon a <color=Highlight>Phantasmic Imprint - Middle<\/color>.n<size=10><\/size>n<size=40><color=Title>Resonance Skill - Stroke of Genius<\/color><\/size>nWhen a <color=Highlight>Phatasmic Imprint<\/color> is nearby, the Resonance Skill is replaced with <color=Highlight>Stroke of Genius<\/color>, which can be cast while in mid-air. When it is cast, Zhezhi will:n-Move to the location of the <color=Highlight>Phatasmic Imprint<\/color>, remove it, and then summon an Ivory Herald to attack the target, dealing <color=Ice>Glacio DMG<\/color>, considered as Basic Attack DMG. Refresh the mid-air Dodge attempts if the target <color=Highlight>Phatasmic Imprint<\/color> is in mid-air.n-Gain 1 stack of Painter's Delight, lasting for 8s and stacking up to 2 times.n<size=10><\/size>n<size=40><color=Title>Resonance Skill - Creation's Zenith<\/color><\/size>nWhen a <color=Highlight>Phantasmic Imprint<\/color> is nearby and there are 2 stacks of Painter's Delight, <color=Highlight>Stroke of Genius<\/color> is replaced with <color=Highlight>Creation's Zenith<\/color>, which can be cast while in mid-air. When it is cast, Zhezhi will:n-Lose all stacks of Painter's Delightn-Move to the location of the <color=Highlight>Phantasmic Imprint<\/color>, remove it, and then summon an Ivory Herald to attack the target, dealing greater <color=Ice>Glacio DMG<\/color>, considered as Basic Attack DMG, additionally increasing the Basic Attack DMG Bonus by 18% for 27s. Refresh the mid-air Dodge attempts if the target <color=Highlight>Phatasmic Imprint<\/color> is in mid-air.n<size=10><\/size>n<size=40><color=Title>Afflatus<\/color><\/size>nZhezhi can hold up to 90 Afflatus.nNormal Attacks grant Afflatus on hit.nCasting Intro Skill grants Afflatus."
